(153, 'yith_maintenance_message', '<h3>OOPS! WE ARE NOT READY YET!</h3>\r\n<p>Hello there! We are not ready yet, but why don''t you leave your email address  and we''ll let you know  as soon as we''re in business!</p>', 'yes'),
