0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:12656:"<p>Nowadays, being on the web with your own commercial activity could be even more important to overcome the ruthless competitors, and to be known by those cozily sat in front of a PC.</p>\n<p dir="ltr">As accurate marketing studies proved, it is clear that, now more than ever, clients are even more selective and pretentious, they care about details. <span id="more-634453"></span> This is why having a place for you online, even a small one, can represent that extra oomph for your business: because when your client will sit in front of a screen, looking for a place to go in the night, you will be immediately visible!</p>\n<p dir="ltr">What we introduce here are the<strong> best Restaurant &amp; Food themes for WordPress</strong> on the market: choose the one that suits the best to your needs and build your own website.<br />\nFor a restaurant, a caf, or a pizzeria, you will understand how easily you can create your project thanks to the numerous options that themes offer.</p>\n<p dir="ltr">Make a presentation of your place, and create a blog page where you can<strong> display your products and your recipes</strong>: choose among the available page layout, show your pictures with wonderful sliders, or with unique and elegant animated effects. If presentation is important, you will hit the bull&#8217;s eye.</p>\n<p dir="ltr">The themes we are introducing are suitable also for who doesn&#8217;t have experience in developing, as the control panel will give the freedom to shape the page without touching the code. Choose the font, the color, the size and the justification of your texts, assemble the header as you want, and use the various shortcodes to create quickly your page.</p>\n<p dir="ltr">The list of the theme we have includes both corporate themes and e-commerce ones.With a Restaurant &amp; Food e-commerce theme, you can create your online atelier, with a platform to sell your products, whichever they may be. Moreover, there would be a product detail page easy to customize, and an intuitive and clear purchase procedure for users.</p>\n<p dir="ltr">Your site will be visible at any resolution; no content will be twisted, as the themes are responsive and compatible with the most famous browsers.Here you are the<strong> best 23+ Restaurant &amp; Food themes</strong> to guide you in the best selection and take the leap to the success.</p>\n<p dir="ltr">Also take a look at our previous articles onshowcases</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a title=" creative WooCommerce themes" href="http://yithemes.com/blog/showcases/best-creative-woocommerce-themes/" target="_blank">20+ Best creative WooCommerce themes for your shop</a></li>\n<li><a title="WordPress Photography Themes" href="http://yithemes.com/blog/showcases/wordpress-photography-themes/">25+ Best WordPress Photography Themes</a></li>\n<li><a title=" Real Estate WordPress Themes" href="http://yithemes.com/blog/showcases/25-best-real-estate-wordpress-themes/">25+ Best Real Estate WordPress Themes</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 style="margin-top: 40px;">PANAREA</h2>\n<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-634605" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/panarea.jpg" alt="panarea" width="870" height="300" /></p>\n<p dir="ltr" style="text-align: center;"><a class="download-link" title="Download File" href="http://yithemes.com/?ddownload=738618">Download</a><a href="http://live.yithemes.com/panarea/"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-38935" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/live.png" alt="live" width="241" height="64" /></a></p>\n<h2 style="margin-top: 40px;">BORDEAUX</h2>\n<div style="text-align: center;"><br />\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-634561" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/bordeaux2.jpg" alt="bordeaux" width="870" height="300" /><br />\n<a class="btn btn-ghost-blue" href="http://demo.orange-themes.com/?theme=339458" rel="nofollow">Live demo</a>\n</div>\n<h2 style="margin-top: 40px;">BARNELLI</h2>\n<div style="text-align: center;">\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-634563" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/barnelli1.jpg" alt="barnelli" width="870" height="300" /><br />\n<a class="btn btn-ghost-blue" href="http://demo.yosoftware.com/" rel="nofollow">Live demo</a></div>\n<h2>CAFETERIA</h2>\n<div style="text-align:center">\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-634565" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/cafeteria1.jpg" alt="cafeteria" width="870" height="300" /><br />\n<a class="btn btn-ghost-blue" href="http://themeforest.net/item/cafeteria-responsive-wordpress-theme/full_screen_preview/6500921" rel="nofollow">live demo</a>\n</div>\n<h2>VICTORIA</h2>\n<div style="text-align: center;">\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-634568" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/victoria1.jpg" alt="victoria" width="870" height="300" /><br />\n<a class="btn btn-ghost-blue" href="http://themeforest.net/item/victoria-premium-restaurant-wordpress-theme/full_screen_preview/1058727" rel="nofollow">live demo</a></div>\n<h2>SUSHI</h2>\n<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-634574" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/sushi1.jpg" alt="sushi" width="870" height="300" /></p>\n<div style="text-align: center;"><a class="btn btn-ghost-blue" href="http://wedesignthemes.com/themes/index.php?theme=sushi" rel="nofollow">live demo</a></div>\n<h2>MILANO</h2>\n<div style="text-align: center;">\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-634576" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/milano1.jpg" alt="milano" width="870" height="300" /><br />\n<a class="btn btn-ghost-blue" href="http://themeforest.net/item/milano-portfolio-photography-hotel-restaurant/full_screen_preview/5939980" rel="nofollow">Live demo</a></div>\n<h2 style="margin-top: 40