s woocommerce theme" width="870" height="400" /><a class="btn btn-ghost-blue" href="http://themes.ishyoboy.com/leepho/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">live demo</a></div>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:73:"http://yithemes.com/blog/showcases/best-creative-woocommerce-themes/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"2";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:42:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:43:"Panarea  E-commerce food wordpress theme";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:77:"http://yithemes.com/blog/free-themes/panarea-e-commerce-food-wordpress-theme/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:86:"http://yithemes.com/blog/free-themes/panarea-e-commerce-food-wordpress-theme/#comments";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Tue, 13 Jan 2015 13:00:48 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:11:"Free Themes";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:29:"http://yithemes.com/?p=632731";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:325:"A dinner in a local traditional restaurant, triumph of the Italian gastronomy, in an elegant and refined background, located in a place where the brightness of the sun joins the flavor of the land, where the panorama that surrounds you seems to be translatable in a sweet melody. This is how Panarea arises, our new [&#8230;]";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:7:"Alessio";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:7476:"<p dir="ltr">A dinner in a local traditional restaurant, triumph of the Italian gastronomy, in an elegant and refined background, located in a place where the brightness of the sun joins the flavor of the land, where the panorama that surrounds you seems to be translatable in a sweet melody.</p>\n<p><span id="more-632731"></span></p>\n<p dir="ltr">This is how Panarea arises, our new eCommerce theme, a tribute to the Sicilian isle with the same name that housed us. A Restaurant &amp; Food theme, for the lovers of gastronomic products and more, that will give you the freedom to make your site a polished online atelier.<!--more--></p>\n<p dir="ltr">With Panarea, you are able to create the site for your restaurant you have always dreamed of, a theme tailored for who wants to be on the web with his own place and innovative offers.</p>\n<p dir="ltr" style="text-align: center;"><a class="download-link" title="Download File" href="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/delightful-downloads/2015/01/panarea-free.zip">Download for free</a><a href="http://live.yithemes.com/panarea/"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-38935" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/live.png" alt="live" width="241" height="64" /></a></p>\n<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-654347 aligncenter" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/screen11.jpg" alt="screen1" width="870" height="400" /></p>\n<h2>PANAREA GENERAL FEATURES</h2>\n<p dir="ltr">Panarea is a highly efficient theme for WordPress platforms that let you create your site easily and quickly, transforming it in an eCommerce site thanks to WooCommerce, the powerful plugin on which the shop is based.</p>\n<p dir="ltr">This project represents a considerable evolution for the Yithemes universe: it is the first theme built with the new YITH framework.<br />\nNow speed and fluidity parameters of the theme are considerably enhanced, getting the wonderful results for which we have worked for many months.</p>\n<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-654428 aligncenter" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/framework.jpg" alt="Yithtmes New Framework" width="870" height="400" /></p>\n<h2>PANAREA CUSTOM HEADER</h2>\n<p dir="ltr">The header is the fundamental point of your project: it must be charming and perfect in every single detail. To do this, you can customize it freely as you wish thanks to the huge variety of options that will be available.</p>\n<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-654369 aligncenter" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/headerTO.jpg" alt="Theme Option header" width="870" height="400" /></p>\n<h2>CREATE YOUR PROJECTS</h2>\n<p dir="ltr">Gather your projects, your ideas, your works and fulfill them in the way that you feel is most appropriate, choosing between a three or four-column layout.</p>\n<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-654374 aligncenter" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/portfolio.jpg" alt="portfolio" width="870" height="520" /></p>\n<h2>CUSTOM PAGES</h2>\n<p dir="ltr">With Panarea you can build your pages easily and pleasantly: thanks to the Visual Composer plugin, that we give you as a gift, you can organize your pages as you want, and with 100 and more shortcodes, you will get to the result in no time!</p>\n<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-654382 aligncenter" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/about.jpg" alt="about" width="870" height="500" /></p>\n<h2>TESTIMONIAL AND FAQ PAGE</h2>\n<p dir="ltr">A powerful shop theme, but also a fluid and elegant corporate theme.<br />\nMake the perfect site for your restaurant with Panarea: take advantage of the FAQ and Testimonial page templates to provide answers to the most frequently asked questions of the people who follow you, and publish quotations of satisfied customers.</p>\n<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-654385 aligncenter" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/faq.jpg" alt="faq page" width="870" height="500" /></p>\n<h2>SLIDERS</h2>\n<p dir="ltr">A slider always let you give a sense of dynamism to the page, and Panarea gives you both the Flexi Slider,Banner Slider and the Parallax slider: three interesting options that you can add in the header of the page, or as content using shortcodes.</p>\n<h2>BLOG</h2>\n<p dir="ltr">Show your article in the Blog page, the reference point for who will visit your site.</p>\n<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-654401 aligncenter" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/blog.jpg" alt="blog page" width="870" height="470" /></p>\n<h2>CUSTOMIZED LOGIN</h2>\n<p dir="ltr">Panarea leaves nothing to chance and give you the freedom to have a totally customized login page.</p>\n<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-654405 aligncenter" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/login.jpg" alt="custom login" width="870" height="300" /></p>\n<h2>PANAREA SHOP</h2>\n<p dir="ltr">If you want your site to be an online atelier, Panarea can have that extra oomph. Elegance, delicacy and functionalities distinguish the page where the products on sale are shown; also, it can count on the sidebar features.</p>\n<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-654415 aligncenter" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/shop.jpg" alt="shop" width="870" height="470" /></p>\n<h2>DETAIL PRODUCT PAGE</h2>\n<p dir="ltr">Panarea let you customize the colors of the product detail page and show the options you want. You can show the Add to cart button or remove it, making every page a simple catalogue page.</p>\n<p dir="ltr">Moreover, you can give the opportunity to users to gather the products they like the most in their wishlist through the specific button, or to compare two or more products with the Compare feature. In addition to that, the image can be zoomed, and you will be free to browse through the related products.</p>\n<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-654423 aligncenter" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/shopDetail.jpg" alt="Shop Detail Page" width="870" height="470" /></p>\n<h2>OPTIMIZED SEO</h2>\n<p dir="ltr">Publishing your site could not be enough, online competitors are ruthless and being among the first results of a research could be an arduous accomplishment.<br />\nThis is why Panarea will let you choose the title, the description and the keywords in detail for every page and every single product in the SEO panel that you can find on WordPress..</p>\n<h2>SAMPLE DATA</h2>\n<p dir="ltr">Import with just one click everything you see in our preview with the Backup and reset plugin you can find within the theme.</p>\n<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-654449 aligncenter" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/backup.jpg" alt="backup" width="870" height="470" /></p>\n<h2>CONCLUSIONS</h2>\n<p dir="ltr">With Panarea your website will be visible at any resolution, from desktop PC to smartphones and laptops, without losing the style you decided to carved in your project.<br />\nWhat are you waiting for, buy Panarea&#8230; now!</p>\n<p dir="ltr" style="text-align: center;"><a class="download-link" title="Download File" href="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/delightful-downloads/2015/01/panarea-free.zip">Download for free</a><a href="http://live.yithemes.com/panarea/"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-38935" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/live.png" alt="live" width="241" height="64" /></a></p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:82:"http://yithemes.com/blog/free-themes/panarea-e-commerce-food-wordpress-theme/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"1";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:42:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:40:"Christmas Bundle : 4 themes for only $99";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:51:"http://yithemes.com/blog/yit-news/christmas-bundle/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:60:"http://yithemes.com/blog/yit-news/christmas-bundle/#comments";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Tue, 16 Dec 2014 13:22:52 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:8:"YIT News";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:29:"http://yithemes.com/?p=706107";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:314:"The snow is falling softly on the tops of the trees, sweet melodies are filling the illuminated houses, now shinier than the rest of the year, and the atmosphere is full of happiness and harmony: this is December, a magic month! A crowding of holidays is coming, and people are running to buy presents: a [&#8230;]";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:7:"Alessio";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:3528:"<div id="christmas-bundle">\n<p dir="ltr">The snow is falling softly on the tops of the trees, sweet melodies are filling the illuminated houses, now shinier than the rest of the year, and the atmosphere is full of happiness and harmony: this is <strong>December</strong>, a magic month!<span id="more-706107"></span><br />\nA crowding of holidays is coming, and people are running to buy presents: a ceremony where we want to take part, to give a careful thought after a year of sacrifices.<br />\nEven for us of <strong>Yithemes</strong> the Christmas season is magic, and it represents the end of a year in which we grew more and more with almost 45,000 users: that is why we have decided to conclude the year with a striking offer never seen before!</p>\n<p><strong>From now until 31th December</strong> you can purchase four themes with only <strong>99$</strong> instead of <strong>260$!</strong><br />\nOur menu is composed by 4 tasty themes, they are similar yet different: <strong>Panthea</strong>, <strong>Socute</strong>, <strong>Jakobi</strong> and <strong>Globe</strong>.</p>\n<p dir="ltr">The first two are well-known: two e-commerce themes renowned as symbols of security and reliability with a following of hundreds of happy and satisfied customers.</p>\n<p class="regular-price">REGULAR PRICE<br />\n<span style="text-decoration: line-through;">$260</span></p>\n<p class="sale-price">XMAS <strong>ONLY $99</strong></p>\n<div class="wrap-bundle-button"><a class="landing-add-to-cart btn btn-beetle-bus-goes-jamba-juice-5 double"><i class="icon-shopping-cart"></i><span class="primary">ADD TO CART</span></a></div>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Promotion expired!</strong></p>\n<h2 dir="ltr">PANTHEA <a href="http://www.yithemes.com/live/?theme=panthea" target="_blank">(Live Demo)</a></h2>\n<p><img class="alignleft" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/panthea_840-221-2.jpg" alt="" width="840" height="221" /></p>\n<h2 dir="ltr">SOCUTE <a href="http://www.yithemes.com/live/?theme=socute" target="_blank">(Live Demo)</a></h2>\n<p><img class="alignleft" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/socute_840-221_07.jpg" alt="" width="840" height="221" /></p>\n<p dir="ltr">On the other hand, Jakobi and Globe represent our last evolution: true gems in design and functionalities. A One Page and an e-commerce will let you understand the importance of having a theme rich of features and easy to use to complete quickly your project!</p>\n<h2 dir="ltr">JAKOBI <a href="http://live.yithemes.com/jakobi" target="_blank">(Live Demo)</a></h2>\n<p><img class="alignleft" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/jakobi_840-221.jpg" alt="" width="840" height="221" /></p>\n<h2 dir="ltr">GLOBE <a href="http://live.yithemes.com/globe" target="_blank">(Live Demo) </a></h2>\n<p><img class="alignleft" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/globe_840-2211.jpg" alt="" width="840" height="221" /></p>\n<p dir="ltr">It is a tempting opportunity to seize, but please, see the demos of our themes and download the free versions if you are puzzled about it.</p>\n<p class="regular-price">REGULAR PRICE <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">$260</span></p>\n<p class="sale-price">XMAS <strong>ONLY $99</strong></p>\n<div class="wrap-bundle-button"><a class="landing-add-to-cart btn btn-beetle-bus-goes-jamba-juice-5 double"><i class="icon-shopping-cart"></i><span class="primary">ADD TO CART</span></a></div>\n</div>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Promotion expired!</strong></p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:56:"http://yithemes.com/blog/yit-news/christmas-bundle/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:2:"16";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}}}s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:1:{s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:3:{s:4:"href";s:25:"http://yithemes.com/feed/";s:3:"rel";s:4:"self";s:4:"type";s:19:"application/rss+xml";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:44:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/";a:2:{s:12:"updatePeriod";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:6:"hourly";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:15:"updateFrequency";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"1";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}}}}}}}}s:4:"type";i:128;s:7:"headers";a:14:{s:6:"server";s:11:"nginx admin";s:4:"date";s:29:"Mon, 02 Mar 2015 02:56:57 GMT";s:12:"content-type";s:23:"text/xml; charset=UTF-8";s:10:"connection";s:5:"c